      "description": "Hey there! It truly breaks my heart to see this beauty go, but it's time for her to find a new home. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always kept in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every Sunday. It\u2019s in absolutely stunning shape, practically looking like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There might be a tiny, tiny speck here or there from a Sunday drive, but honestly, you won\u2019t find another one this clean. It runs like a dream and turns heads everywhere. Come by, let's grab a coffee, and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
